ftestSetNameOfGame( factorize, `"
Usage: factorize [<options>] [<envSpec>] <f> [<v>]
  factorizes canonical form <f>.
  If algebraic variable <v> is specified, factorizes in
  algebraic extension by <v>.
"'`' )

//{{{ docu
